sourcesContent: import React from "react"; const EditableData = ({ data }) => { const styles = { backgroundColor: "#EEEEEE", border: "none", height: "30px", }; const errStyles = { borderColor: "red", }; const [fieldsFilled, setFieldsFilled] = useState(null); const checkFields = () => { if ( title === "" || address === "" || longituide === "" || latitude === "" || startTime === "" || endTime === "" || postalCode === "" || category === "" || category === "Select a Category" || phone === "" || fb === "" || insta === "" || twitter === "" || url === "" || email === "" ) { setFieldsFilled(false); } else { setFieldsFilled(true); } }; return ( ); }; export default EditableData;
